<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>URL Shortener</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2e6dc;
            /* soft pastel beige */
        }

        /* Navbar */
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            background-color: #f2e6dc;

        }

        .navbar button {
            margin-left: 15px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border: 2px solid #00a6a6;
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #00a6a6;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar button:hover {
            background-color: #00a6a6;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Main container */
        .container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 40px 40px;
        }

        .description {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .description h1 {
            font-size: 44px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #b23b3b;
        }

        .description p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .image img {
            max-width: 500px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #f2e6dc;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #5e5e5e;

        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <div class="navbar">
        <button onclick="location.href='/login'">Login</button>
        <button onclick="location.href='/signup'">Sign Up</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="description">
            <h1>Simplify Your Links</h1>
            <p>
                Welcome to our URL Shortener – the smart way to shrink long, complicated URLs into short,
                shareable links. Whether you're a marketer, developer, or casual user, our tool makes
                link management a breeze.
            </p>
            <p>
                ✦ Create clean, compact links in seconds.<br>
                ✦ Track click stats in real-time.<br>
                ✦ Customize your short URLs with keywords.<br>
                ✦ Perfect for social media, blogs, and emails.
            </p>
            <p>
                No more clunky URLs – just short, smart, and simple!
            </p>
            <p><strong>This site is made by Soumita Banerjee.</strong></p>
        </div>


        <div class="image">
            <img src="/images/images3.png" alt="URL Shortener Illustration">
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        &copy; 2025 Soumita Banerjee | All rights reserved.
    </footer>

</body>

</html>